early_stopping = tf.keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(monitor='val_acc', patience=20)
save_weights = tf.keras.callbacks.ModelCheckpoint(os.path.join(data_dir, "checkpoint.hdf5"),
                                                  monitor='val_acc',
                                                  verbose=1,
                                                  save_best_only=True,
                                                  mode="max",
                                                  save_freq="epoch",
                                                  save_weights_only=True)
csv_logger = tf.keras.callbacks.CSVLogger(os.path.join(data_dir, "train_log.csv"))

* tf.keras.layers.Layer vs. tf.keras.Model 차이

비슷한 API를 쓰지만 Model 클래스는 model.fit(), model.predict(), model.evaluate()를 쓸 수 있다.

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/55109696/tensorflow-difference-between-tf-keras-layers-layer-vs-tf-keras-model
